"The output (convex hull) vector layer. Other than the input attributes, the "
"output layer also contains the following fields: ``area`` and ``perimeter`` "
"of the generated polygon."
msgstr ""
"Il layer vettoriale in uscita (poligono convesso). Oltre agli attributi in "
"ingresso, il layer in uscita contiene anche i seguenti campi: ``area`` e "
"``perimetro`` del poligono generato."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1515
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:convexhull``"
msgstr "**ID Algoritmo**: ``native:convexhull``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1525
msgid "Create wedge buffers"
msgstr "Crea buffer a spicchi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1526
msgid "Creates wedge shaped buffers from input points."
msgstr "Crea buffer a forma di spicchio dai punti in ingresso."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1531
msgid "Wedge buffers"
msgstr "Buffer a spicchio"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1533
msgid ""
"The native output from this algorithm are CurvePolygon geometries, but these"
" may be automatically segmentized to Polygons depending on the output "
"format."
msgstr ""
"Il risultato finale di questo algoritmo sono geometrie CurvePolygon, ma "
"queste possono essere automaticamente segmentate in Poligoni a seconda del "
"formato in uscita."

