#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5247
msgid "``WIDTH``"
msgstr "``WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1566
