msgstr ":ref:`qgisbufferbym`, :ref:`qgisbuffer`, :ref:`qgiswedgebuffers`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7019
msgid "**Start width**"
msgstr "**Larghezza iniziale**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7020
msgid "``START_WIDTH``"
msgstr "``START_WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7024
msgid ""
"Represents the radius of the buffer applied at the start point of the line "
"feature"
msgstr ""
"Rappresenta il raggio del buffer applicato al punto iniziale dell'elemento "
"lineare."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7026
msgid "**End width**"
msgstr "**Larghezza finale**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7027
msgid "``END_WIDTH``"
msgstr "``END_WIDTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7031
msgid ""
"Represents the radius of the buffer applied at the end point of the line "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"Rappresenta il raggio del buffer applicato al punto finale dell'elemento "
"lineare."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7037
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7393
msgid "Default: 16"
msgstr "Predefinito: 16"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7072
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:taperedbuffer``"
msgstr "**ID Algoritmo**: ``native:taperedbuffer``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7082
msgid "Tessellate"
msgstr "Mosaicatura"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7083
msgid ""
"Tessellates a polygon geometry layer, dividing the geometries into "
"triangular components."
msgstr "Tassella un vettore poligonale, dividendo le geometrie in triangoli."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7086
msgid ""
"The output layer consists of multipolygon geometries for each input feature,"
" with each multipolygon consisting of multiple triangle component polygons."
msgstr ""
"Il risultato consiste in geometrie multipoligonali per ogni elemento in "
"ingresso, con ogni multi poligono costituito da poligoni triangolari."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7093
msgid "Tessellated polygon (right)"
msgstr "Poligono tassellato (destra)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7115
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7139
msgid "**Tesselated**"
msgstr "**Tassellato**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7142
